Deciding to follow, Sanguine aka Lizzie entered maximal base. It was a 
definitively good thing, because she could infiltrate and learn more 
before sowing chaos...

Taking on a childish tone, she went after Amperion.

Sanguine: Amperion!?! It's no time to play hide and seek! Com'on! 
Let's follow that lady!

She couldn't exactly remember why, but she thought she remembered that 
Empath from somewhere. Maybe they had met before in a predacon context 
or that she had seen her somewhere. She would do well to investigate.
